text: Serratifusus is a genus of sea snails, marine gastropod mollusks in the family Buccinidae, the true whelks. ==Species== Species within the genus Serratifusus include: * Serratifusus excelens Fraussen Hadorn, 2003 * Serratifusus harasewychi Fraussen Hadorn, 2003 * Serratifusus sitanius Fraussen Hadorn, 2003 ==References== Category:Buccinidae
title: Serratifusus
